        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_1",
          "href": null,
          "name": "4628",
          "text": "When I wrote this article, I had no idea how far it would go!",
          "metadata": {
            "id": "1*J2kpss8Y94x57YTaw-QvNg.png",
            "alt": null
          },
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": "INSET_CENTER",
          "markups": [],
          "type": "IMG"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "900b",
          "text": "Many of you have discovered my work in the last few weeks as I wrote a series of articles about the global crisis — focusing on the desperate need for cultural healing at the heart of it all.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "943b",
          "text": "One of these articles has now been read by several hundred thousand people, spreading organically across social media as people read and shared it with their friends. How did I do it?",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
              "end": 21,
              "href": "https://medium.com/@joe_brewer/the-mental-disease-of-late-stage-capitalism-4a7bb2a1411c#.gowquf6vt",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 0,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_4",
          "href": null,
          "name": "767e",
          "text": "The answer may surprise you. It certainly surprised me! This was the culmination of many years engaged in my own healing process, while at the same time studying and learning about the global systems and patterns giving rise to the future of humanity in this period of unprecedented planetary-scale change.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_5",
          "href": null,
          "name": "f4b4",
          "text": "I wrote the article in 45 minutes, as part of an unfolding series of commentaries on systemic corruption and the healing that is needed to dismantle the architecture of wealth extraction worldwide. But I was not prepared for the wave of humanity washing over me as the article went viral, then began trending, and has now been republished in many places while continuing to spread today.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_6",
          "href": null,
          "name": "ab2a",
          "text": "A dear friend asked me to share my story of the writing process and how I wrote so prolifically (nearly a dozen articles in less than two weeks), building up a web of thoughts, feelings, and new relationships that kept the stories going as more people came into the fold.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_7",
          "href": null,
          "name": "6226",
          "text": "That story is shared in this one-hour podcast:",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "f24884a6d869_8",
          "href": null,
          "name": "e14c",
          "text": "",
          "metadata": {
