          "href": null,
          "name": "8cba",
          "text": "I hope these reflections will help you on your learning journey. The world is changing quickly now and we need a great awakening to our shared humanity. The ability to see systemic patterns across our personal lives that weave us into a global whole is fundamental and essential for all the work we must do together in the years ahead.",
